## The breaking point

```elixir
import Kernel, except: [-: 1, +: 2, -: 2, *: 2, /: 2, <>: 2]
import Surreal

# BE WARNED! vvv Executing this line will consume all your RAM
nine = to_surreal(3) * to_surreal(3)
IO.inspect(nine)
nine |> to_number
```

